    "source": "import { MapEntry } from './hash_map'\n\n/**\n * This interface is a representation of the Map data structure.\n */\nexport interface Map<K, V> {\n  getSize(): number\n  set(key: K, value: V): void\n  get(key: K): V | null\n  delete(key: K): void\n  has(key: K): boolean\n  clear(): void\n  keys(): K[]\n  values(): V[]\n  entries(): MapEntry<K, V>[]\n}\n",
